WEBVTT

00:00:59.590 --> 00:01:00.996
ta'sir ko'rsatadi.

00:01:00.996 --> 00:01:03.277
Depressiyada turlicha 
alomatlar kuzatilishi

00:01:03.277 --> 00:01:04.281
mumkin: tushkun

00:01:04.281 --> 00:01:06.912
kayfiyat, odatiy 
yoqtirgan narsalariga

00:01:06.912 --> 00:01:08.485
qizishning so'nishi, ishtahadagi

00:01:08.485 --> 00:01:10.835
o'zgarishlar, o'zini keraksiz va
o'ta gunohkor

00:01:10.835 --> 00:01:13.531
his qilish ortiqcha yoki o'ta kam uyqu,

00:01:13.531 --> 00:01:15.363
diqqatning pasayishi,

00:01:15.363 --> 00:01:17.198
bezovtalik yoki harakat sustligi

00:01:17.198 --> 00:01:18.681
darmonsizlanish, yoki

00:01:18.681 --> 00:01:21.215
o’z joniga qasd qilishni
beto'xtov o'ylash.

00:01:21.215 --> 00:01:23.461
Psixiatrik qo’llanmalari
bo'yicha sizda bu

00:01:23.461 --> 00:01:25.445
alomatlarning kamida beshtasi mavjudligi

00:01:25.445 --> 00:01:28.924
sizga depressiya tashxisini qo’yadi.

00:01:28.924 --> 00:01:31.292
U faqat xulq-atvor alomatlaridangina
iborat emas.